{"source": "https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/jingmao/gt1-05102023025241.html", "type": "NewsArticle", "published time": "2023-05-10T02:55:00-04:00", "modified time": "2023-05-10T12:30:38-04:00", "author": null, "publisher": {"type": "Organization", "name": "Radio Free Asia"}, "title": "\u5fae\u8f6f\u65d7\u4e0b\u9886\u82f1\u6c42\u804c\u5e73\u53f0\u9000\u51fa\u4e2d\u56fd\u5e02\u573a", "description": "\u5fae\u8f6f\u516c\u53f8\u65d7\u4e0b\u7684\u793e\u4ea4\u5a92\u4f53\u9886\u82f1\u5ba3\u5e03\uff0c\u5c06\u5173\u95ed\u4e2d\u56fd\u7684\u6c42\u804c\u5e94\u7528\u5e73\u53f0\u3002\u9886\u82f1\u8868\u793a\uff0c\u7531\u4e8e\u6fc0\u70c8\u7684\u7ade\u4e89\u548c\u5145\u6ee1\u6311\u6218\u7684\u5b8f\u89c2\u7ecf\u6d4e\u73af\u5883\uff0c\u5b83\u5c06\u505c\u6b62\u4e2d\u56fd\u7684\u6c42\u804c\u5e94\u7528\u670d\u52a1\u3002", "videos": [], "audios": ["https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/jingmao/gt1-05102023025241.html/@@stream"], "text": "<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/jingmao/gt1-05102023025241.html/@@images/210c3936-9d5b-444e-bd9b-2217a53927ee.jpeg\"/>\n\u62e5\u67095700\u4e07\u4e2d\u56fd\u4f1a\u5458\u7684\u9886\u82f1\u516c\u53f8\u5ba3\u5e038\u6708\u5173\u95ed\u4e2d\u56fd\u793e\u4ea4\u5e73\u53f0\u3002\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/jingmao/gt1-05102023025241.html/@@images/image\">\n</a>\n\u8def\u900f\n<!-- zoomattribute -->\n<script language=\"javascript\" type=\"text/javascript\">\n var audio_title = {\"audio_name\": \"\\u5fae\\u8f6f\\u65d7\\u4e0b\\u9886\\u82f1\\u6c42\\u804c\\u5e73\\u53f0\\u9000\\u51fa\\u4e2d\\u56fd\\u5e02\\u573a\"};\n</script>\n<script>\n eventer = function(id){\n            var data = {\n                    \"tealium_event\" : \"audio_play\",\n                    \"on_page_event\" : \"audio_play\",\n                    \"audio_name\": audio_title['audio_name'],\n                    \"article_uid\": utag_data[\"article_uid\"],\n                    \"media_type\": \"onDemand audio\",\n                    \"media_name\